featured_reviews.review_id:
Masjid Bhola Shah Sahab  msjid bholaa shaah saahb is located in Khaai pada , Baran . Alhamdulillah after new construction the capacity of this masjid extended. Now it's bacame ground plus two stories masjid.
Khutba of Juma starts here at 13:35 o'clock in this masjid. So if you wants to offer your Juma salaah here in this masjid than reach here before 1:35 p.m.
Jazaak Allahu Khairaa.. May Allah s.w.t. rewards you aptly for reading my review.
